it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface MapView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataWidget, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, MultiDataWidget, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Widget

    public interface MapView
extends DataWidget, MultiDataWidget
    A representation of the model object 'Map View'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Map Id
    • Start Envelope Spec
    • Max Envelope Spec
    • Scale Envelope Spec
    • Num Levels
    • Edit Data Binding
    • Gadgets
    • No Click When Disabled
    • No Edit When Disabled
    • No Zoom When Disabled
    • No Pan When Disabled
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getMapView()

      • isNoClickWhenDisabled

        boolean isNoClickWhenDisabled()
        Returns the value of the 'No Click When Disabled' attribute. The default value is "true". Se impostato a true quando il widget è disabilitato viene disabilitato anche un eventuale possibilità di scatenare un evento di click sulla mappa
        Returns:
        the value of the 'No Click When Disabled' attribute.
